org.ietf.nea.pa.attribute

Class PaAttributeValueRemediationParametersBuilderIetf

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.ietf.nea.pa.attribute.PaAttributeValueRemediationParametersBuilderIetf
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ImAttributeValueBuilder, TransmissionObjectBuilder<ImAttributeValue>, PaAttributeValueRemediationParametersBuilder

    public class PaAttributeValueRemediationParametersBuilderIetf
extends Object
implements PaAttributeValueRemediationParametersBuilder
    Builder to build an integrity measurement remediation parameters attribute value compliant to RFC 5792. It evaluates the given values and can be used in a fluent way.
